### EscrowPay — VS Code REST Client
### Install extension: humao.rest-client
### Set @token below after logging in

@base = http://localhost:8000
@token = PASTE_YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
@order_id = PASTE_ORDER_ID_HERE

### ─── AUTH ────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Signup - Customer
POST {{base}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Customer",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "secret123",
  "role": "customer"
}

###

### Signup - Seller
POST {{base}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bob Seller",
  "email": "bob@example.com",
  "password": "secret123",
  "role": "seller"
}

###

### Login (copy token from response → paste into @token above)
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

###

### Get Current User
GET {{base}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List All Sellers
GET {{base}}/auth/sellers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ─── ORDERS ────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create Order (use a seller id from /auth/sellers)
POST {{base}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "seller_id": "SELLER_UUID_HERE",
  "amount": 1500.00,
  "description": "Electronics delivery"
}

###

### List My Orders
GET {{base}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get Order by ID
GET {{base}}/orders/{{order_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Mark Delivered (seller token required)
POST {{base}}/orders/{{order_id}}/deliver
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Dashboard Analytics
GET {{base}}/orders/analytics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ─── ESCROW ────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Deposit to Escrow
POST {{base}}/escrow/deposit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "order_id": "{{order_id}}"
}

###

### Release Payment (confirm delivery)
POST {{base}}/escrow/release
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "order_id": "{{order_id}}"
}

###

### Raise Dispute
POST {{base}}/escrow/dispute
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "order_id": "{{order_id}}"
}

###

### Request Refund
POST {{base}}/escrow/refund
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "order_id": "{{order_id}}"
}

###

### Transaction History
GET {{base}}/escrow/transactions/{{order_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
